name: EVERYDAY Pain Relief Limestone Footbed - Unisex

features: CARBON FIBER STABILIZER CAP: The base of the insole supports the rearfoot and provides structure and stability to the foam layer, reinforced with EVOLyte™, Superfeet’s proprietary carbon fiber & polymer blend.
VIBRAM® DIFLEX THERAPEUTIC FOAM: Dermo-compatible, antifungal and antibacterial, the foam layer shapes to your foot for personalized relief
HEEL STABILIZER: Personalizes the feel and function of the insole. Reduces excessive shifting and movement in the footwear
BEVELED EDGE: The beveled foam edge improves the fit in tighter fitting footwear.
HEEL CUP: Helps position the heel to naturally absorb impact.
